VERSION

HTML::Tmojo Version 0.300

ABSTRACT

Tmojo(tm) is a powerful and flexible content generation
engine developed at Lab-01. For more information, read
docs/nutshell.txt or visit <http://lab-01.com/>.

INSTALLATION

Tmojo comes with a typical Perl installation setup. The
following commands should properly install Tmojo:

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test
  make install

If you have trouble installing Tmojo this way, you can
always just make sure that the contents of the 'lib'
directory are in Perl's @INC array.

